<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Submitted – STAY EMBRACE</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/logo-brow.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="auth-container" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45)), url('/images/pic2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;">
    <div class="auth-card">

        <a href="/register" class="auth-logo-link">
            <img src="/images/logo-head.png" alt="EMBRACE" class="auth-logo-img">
            <span class="auth-logo-text">STAY EMBRACE</span>
        </a>

        <div class="auth-header">
            <div class="role-badge student-badge">STUDENT</div>
            <h2>Registration Submitted</h2>
            <p>Your account is pending admin approval</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pending-message">
            <i class="pending-icon">&#9201;</i>
            <p>Your registration has been received successfully.</p>
            <p>The admin will review and approve your account. Once approved, you will be able to login using your Student ID and password.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-footer">
            Already approved? <a href="/login/student">Login here</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
